Study the Marie architecture as explained in T103_Chapter4.ppt document 
provided in the project folder.

Below are the main steps needed to accomplish this project. Additional 
information can be found on DeepSeek or other AI tools.

Main steps:
 1. Install Linux on Virtual Box, or VMWare, or ...
 2. Download icarus verilog simulator
 3. Download gtkwave waveform viewer 
 4. On the command prompt of a Linux/Unix/Mac Shell, Compile and 
    Run provided sample test as follows:

    %iverilog -f cpu.f	// Compile code
    %vvp a.out		// Run Simulation
    %gtkwave dump.vcd & // View waveform signals
     
 5. Once everything is setup you can implement the project as explained
    in the project.txt file included in the project folder.

